<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>CottonClothing | Premium Fashion</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#f5f7fa;
color:#222;
}

header{
background:#111827;
padding:15px 5%;
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
position:sticky;
top:0;
z-index:100;
}

.logo{
font-size:32px;
font-weight:700;
color:#00d4ff;
}

nav a{
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
margin-left:25px;
font-weight:500;
}

.hero{
height:85vh;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#2563eb);
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
text-align:center;
color:white;
padding:20px;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:60px;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

.hero p{
font-size:22px;
max-width:700px;
}

.btn{
display:inline-block;
margin-top:25px;
padding:15px 35px;
background:white;
color:#2563eb;
font-weight:700;
text-decoration:none;
border-radius:50px;
}

.section{
padding:70px 8%;
}

.section h2{
text-align:center;
margin-bottom:40px;
font-size:38px;
}

.categories{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));
gap:20px;
}

.category{
background:white;
padding:35px;
border-radius:15px;
text-align:center;
box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
font-size:22px;
font-weight:600;
}

.products{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));
gap:25px;
}

.card{
background:white;
border-radius:15px;
overflow:hidden;
box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
transition:.3s;
}

.card:hover{
transform:translateY(-5px);
}

.card img{
width:100%;
height:320px;
object-fit:cover;
}

.info{
padding:20px;
}

.info h3{
margin-bottom:10px;
}

.price{
font-size:24px;
color:green;
font-weight:bold;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

.buy{
display:block;
text-align:center;
padding:12px;
background:#2563eb;
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
border-radius:8px;
}

.about{
background:white;
border-radius:15px;
padding:30px;
line-height:1.8;
box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
}

footer{
background:#111827;
color:white;
text-align:center;
padding:30px;
margin-top:40px;
}

@media(max-width:768px){

.hero h1{
font-size:40px;
}

.hero p{
font-size:18px;
}

nav{
display:none;
}

}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>

<div class="logo">🧵 CottonClothing</div>

<nav>
<a href="#">Home</a>
<a href="#categories">Categories</a>
<a href="#products">Products</a>
<a href="#about">About</a>
</nav>

</header>

<section class="hero">

<h1>CottonClothing</h1>

<p>
Premium Cotton Fashion For Men & Women.
Stylish Designs. Affordable Prices.
</p>

<a href="#products" class="btn">Shop Now</a>

</section>

<section class="section" id="categories">

<h2>Shop By Category</h2>

<div class="categories">

<div class="category">👕 T-Shirts</div>
<div class="category">👔 Shirts</div>
<div class="category">👖 Jeans</div>
<div class="category">🧥 Hoodies</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="section" id="products">

<h2>Trending Products</h2>

<div class="products">

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521572163474-6864f9cf17ab?w=800">
<div class="info">
<h3>Premium Cotton Tee</h3>
<div class="price">₹499</div>
<a class="buy" href="#">Add To Cart</a>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512436991641-6745cdb1723f?w=800">
<div class="info">
<h3>Classic Shirt</h3>
<div class="price">₹899</div>
<a class="buy" href="#">Add To Cart</a>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542272604-787c3835535d?w=800">
<div class="info">
<h3>Denim Jeans</h3>
<div class="price">₹1299</div>
<a class="buy" href="#">Add To Cart</a>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503341504253-dff4815485f1?w=800">
<div class="info">
<h3>Premium Hoodie</h3>
<div class="price">₹1499</div>
<a class="buy" href="#">Add To Cart</a>
</div>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="section" id="about">

<h2>About CottonClothing</h2>

<div class="about">

CottonClothing is an online fashion store focused on
premium cotton apparel, modern designs, and affordable pricing.

We deliver quality clothing directly to customers and continuously
add new collections to keep your wardrobe fresh and stylish.

</div>

</section>

<footer>

<h3>🧵 CottonClothing</h3>
<p>Premium Fashion Store</p>
<p>© 2026 All Rights Reserved</p>

</footer>

</body>
</html>
